// 4. J. Boksansky, "Crash Course in BRDF Implementation," 2021. [Online]. Available: https://boksajak.github.io/blog/BRDF.
// 5. S. Lagarde and C. de Rousiers, "Moving Frostbite to Physically Based Rendering," 2014.
